description.en: Shibonics is a $SHIB reflection token. We believe $SHIB will change the whole crypto space. That’s why we created Shibonics, the little brother of $SHIB, to help $SHIB conquer the Cryptomarket. Every buy in Shibonics will lead to a 1% burn and a 4% reward in $SHIB which goes to the Shibonics holders automatically.
